{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_06_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 莉央への本心",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺が……？　莉央さんの彼氏……ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me…? Rio-san's boyfriend…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　声が大きいわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on! Your voice is too loud!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。でも、本当にそんな風に\n思ってるんですか？　考え過ぎなんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I'm sorry. But it's really like that.\nMaybe you're overthinking it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、絶対勘違いしているわ\n私は娘なのよ。母の思考が手に取るように分かるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ she's definitely misunderstanding something.\nI'm her daughter. I can understand my mother's thoughts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、年頃の娘が若い男性を実家に連れて行く……\nそう思われても仕方のないシチュエーションでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ a girl bringing young man in her age home…\nIt's a situation that could easily lead to such assumptions‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "言われてみればそうかも……うかつでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ maybe you're right… I was careless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "貴方から事務的に話をしてもらえば\n誤解も解けるって思ってたけど……甘かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought that if you spoke to her in a business-like manner‚\nthe misunderstanding would clear up… but I was naive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が、必要以上に私を持ち上げるからよ！？\nだからお母さんのテンションが上がっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because you overly praise me‚ isn't it!?\nThat's why my mother got all excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、俺は莉央さんに対する本心を話したまでです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I've only spoken the truth about how I feel towards Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ほーら出た！　今のよ！\nさらっとそういうことを言わないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See! There it is again!\nDon't say things like that so casually!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういうこと？　どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things like what? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……もういいわ……\n貴方だけが悪いって訳じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Forget it…\nIt's not just your fault either‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんなことばっかり言ってると\nそのうち……誰かの恨みを買う、かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but if you keep saying things like that\neventually‚ you might incur someone's resentment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、怖いこと言わないで下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-Don't say scary things like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく！　私の母は今、娘が彼氏を\n連れて来たって信じ込んで、有頂天なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway! Right now‚ my mother is absolutely convinced\nthat I've brought my boyfriend home‚ and she's overjoyed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "以後、会話には気を付けて\n結婚とか恋愛とかそっち方面の話題にならないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ be careful with your conversations‚\nand avoid any topics related to marriage or romance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、俺も莉央さんももうすぐ東京に戻りますよね\nお母さんに誤解させたままでいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But both you and I will be returning to Tokyo soon‚ right?\nIs it okay to leave your mother with this misunderstanding?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……そうね……。でも、あんなに喜んでいるのに\nもし、本当のことを言ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… You're right… But she's so happy right now…\nIf I tell her the truth…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "お母さん、ちょっと{user}さんの\nことで、話があるんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mom‚ there's something I need to talk about\n{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええっ！？　あの人は莉央の彼氏じゃないの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? That person is not a Rio's boyfriend!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんな……うっ！　急に胸が……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… my chest suddenly…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "――なんてことになったら困るでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――We can't let it come to that! Anyway‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、しばらく黙っておくわ\n時間を掛けて、ソフトに説明しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "let's keep quiet for a while‚ and\nlet's explain it gently over time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\nじゃあ、俺は彼氏のフリをすればいいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood.\nSo‚ I should pretend to be your boyfriend‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。たとえフリでも、私の彼氏なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry even if you're just pretending to be my boyfriend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7666666667,
